Package angryflappybird

Class Defines

java.lang.Object
angryflappybird.Defines
public class Defines extends Object
This class contains all of the coefficients related to the game app, scene, UI, and components. It can initialize all the components and their change images
Author:
Willow Kelleigh and Anh Thach

  • Constructor Details

    • Defines

      Defines()
      This is the constructor for the defines class. It initializes the components of the game It takes in no arguments and returns nothing

  • Method Details

    • pathImage

      public String pathImage(String filepath)
      This is a method to get the filepath of something in the resources/images folder. It is used within the Defines class to initialize the images of the components
      Parameters:
      filepath - The name of the image as it is stored in the resources/images folder
      Returns:
      the full filepath path of the image
